<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:13:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>干邑高管和欧盟官员出席北京白兰地倾销听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cognac-executives-eu-officials-attend-beijing-hearing-brandy-dumping-2024-07-18/</link><description>法国干邑白兰地协会在一份声明中表示，法国干邑白兰地公司高管和欧盟官员周四在北京出席了有关中国对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查的听证会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cognac-executives-eu-officials-attend-beijing-hearing-brandy-dumping-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国共产党罢免最高机构中前外长、国防部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</link><description>据新华社报道，周四，在中国共产党最大的最高层执行机构的一次重要会议上，中国共产党接受了前外交部长秦刚在中央委员会的辞呈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，受客户退出影响，普华永道将大幅削减中国合伙人薪酬</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hit-by-client-exits-pwc-slash-china-partners-pay-sources-say-2024-07-18/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，普华永道 (PwC) 已要求其中国合作伙伴减薪最多 50%，因为对该公司的监管调查以及部分企业客户的离开促使成本削减，裁员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hit-by-client-exits-pwc-slash-china-partners-pay-sources-say-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>台积电第二季度利润增长36% 好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q2-profit-rises-36-better-than-forecast-2024-07-18/</link><description>台湾芯片制造商台积电周四公布第二季度净利润增长 36%，超出市场预期，因人工智能应用中使用的半导体需求激增。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q2-profit-rises-36-better-than-forecast-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着贸易紧张局势加剧，筹码下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-18/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中美芯片战加深，科技股波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</link><description>周四，亚洲芯片股暴跌，而欧洲芯片股则试探性开盘，此前有报道称美国正在考虑对向中国出口先进半导体技术实施更严格的限制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普发表评论后，台湾表示致力于加强防御</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-says-committed-strengthening-defence-after-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</link><description>台湾外交部周四表示，台湾致力于加强防御并与美国合作，几天前，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普被引述称台湾应该为防御付费。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-says-committed-strengthening-defence-after-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪计划在越南积极扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-introduce-three-more-car-models-vietnam-market-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周四概述了积极扩大其在越南经销网络的计划，本周将在越南开设第一家门店，这对当地竞争对手 VinFast 构成了巨大的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:30:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-introduce-three-more-car-models-vietnam-market-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>越南向联合国提出扩展南海大陆架的主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-files-un-claim-extended-continental-shelf-south-china-sea-2024-07-18/</link><description>越南外交部周四表示，在地区邻国菲律宾采取类似行动一个月后，越南已向联合国提出南海扩展大陆架（ECS）主张。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-files-un-claim-extended-continental-shelf-south-china-sea-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着科技股跌幅加深，欧洲等待欧洲央行信号</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-18/</link><description>周四，欧洲交易员试图将股市从科技股主导的暴跌中拉出来，因为人们的注意力转向欧洲央行是否会暗示 9 月份是下一个可能降息的时间点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:02:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>干预紧张导致日元上涨；欧元关注欧洲央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-spikes-spectre-intervention-spooks-investors-2024-07-18/</link><description>日本日元周四升至六周高位，引发了有关官方推动行动的猜测，而交易员则等待欧洲央行会议来指导欧元的下一步走势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-spikes-spectre-intervention-spooks-investors-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>台积电利用人工智能需求提高收入预测，拒绝美国合资企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-stock-pressured-by-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</link><description>鉴于对人工智能芯片的需求激增，全球最大的代工芯片制造商台湾台积电周四上调了全年营收预期，并拒绝了在美国设立合资工厂的想法。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-stock-pressured-by-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>向俄罗斯走私军事技术的男子被判入狱三年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/man-who-smuggled-military-tech-russia-sentenced-3-years-us-jail-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国司法部表示，一名俄罗斯男子周三被判处三年监禁，该男子承认美国指控他向俄罗斯走私大量美国制造的军用级微电子产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/man-who-smuggled-military-tech-russia-sentenced-3-years-us-jail-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：随着科技股下跌、日元飙升，波动性回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-17/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:49:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普国家安全顾问呼吁台湾增加国防开支</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-national-security-adviser-calls-taiwan-lift-defense-spending-2024-07-17/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普的一位高级国家安全顾问周三表示，面对中国潜在的侵略，台湾需要大幅增加国防开支。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-national-security-adviser-calls-taiwan-lift-defense-spending-2024-07-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>